{"config":{"lang":["en"],"separator":"[\\s\\-]+","pipeline":["stopWordFilter"],"fields":{"title":{"boost":1000.0},"text":{"boost":1.0},"tags":{"boost":1000000.0}}},"docs":[{"location":"","title":"<code>Django Facile</code>","text":"<p>Django Facile is a developer-focused CLI tool designed to simplify and automate Django project setup, configuration, and workflows.</p>"},{"location":"#why-django-facile","title":"Why Django Facile?","text":"<p>Setting up Django projects repeatedly involves: - manual configuration - environment setup - repetitive commands - Switching to Production mode</p> <p>Django Facile solves this by providing a single CLI interface.</p>"},{"location":"#key-features","title":"Key Features","text":"<ul> <li>One-command project setup  </li> <li>Dev \u2194 Prod environment switching  </li> <li>Built-in database migration workflow  </li> <li>Developer-friendly commands  </li> <li>Production-ready configuration</li> <li>Automatically configured environment variables  </li> </ul>"},{"location":"#quick-start","title":"Quick Start","text":"<pre><code>django-facile startproject myproject --env dev --db sqlite\ncd myproject\ndjango-facile run\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"commands/","title":"Commands","text":"<p>\u26a0\ufe0f Notes Use virtual environment (recommended) Ensure Python is added to PATH</p>"},{"location":"commands/#commandsmd","title":"<code>commands.md</code>","text":""},{"location":"commands/#startproject","title":"startproject","text":"<p>Create a new Django project.</p> <pre><code>django-facile startproject &lt;project_name&gt; --env dev --db sqlite\n</code></pre> <p>Create a new Django app</p> <pre><code>django-facile startapp &lt;app_name&gt;\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"commands/#switch-environment","title":"switch environment","text":"<pre><code>django-facile switch-env dev   # to development\ndjango-facile switch-env prod  # to production\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"commands/#start-django-development-server","title":"Start django development server","text":"<pre><code>django-facile run\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"commands/#makemigration-migrate-in-one-command","title":"Makemigration &amp; Migrate in one command","text":"<pre><code>django-facile migrate\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"commands/#create-superuser","title":"Create superuser","text":"<pre><code>django-facile superuser\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"commands/#django-shell-for-testing","title":"django shell for testing","text":"<pre><code>django-facile shell\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"commands/#validate-project-configuration","title":"Validate project configuration","text":""},{"location":"commands/#for-development-validation","title":"for development validation","text":"<pre><code>django-facile check\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"commands/#for-production-validation","title":"for production validation","text":"<pre><code>django-facile check --deploy\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"commands/#collect-static-files-for-production","title":"Collect static files for production","text":"<pre><code>django-facile collectstatic\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"commands/#help","title":"help","text":"<pre><code>django-facile --help\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"commands/#version","title":"version","text":"<pre><code>django-facile --version\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"installation/","title":"Installation","text":""},{"location":"installation/#installationmd","title":"<code>installation.md</code>","text":""},{"location":"installation/#create-virtual-env-best-practice","title":"Create virtual env (Best Practice)","text":"<pre><code>python -m venv venv\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"installation/#activate-venv","title":"activate venv","text":""},{"location":"installation/#for-windows","title":"for windows","text":"<pre><code>venv/scripts/activate\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"installation/#for-linux","title":"for linux","text":"<pre><code>source venv/bin/activate\n\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"installation/#install-via-pip","title":"Install via pip","text":"<pre><code>pip install django-facile\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"installation/#verify-the-installation","title":"Verify the installation","text":"<pre><code>django-facile --help\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"installation/#check-version","title":"Check version","text":"<pre><code>django-facile --version\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"installation/#project-structure-after-creating-project","title":"Project structure (After creating project)","text":"<pre><code>myproject/\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 manage.py\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 settings/\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 apps/\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 urls.py\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 asgi.py\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 wsgi.py\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 .env\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 .gitignore\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"workflow/","title":"Workflow","text":""},{"location":"workflow/#workflowmd","title":"<code>workflow.md</code>","text":""},{"location":"workflow/#step-1-create-project","title":"Step 1: Create project","text":""},{"location":"workflow/#step-2-create-app","title":"Step 2: Create app","text":""},{"location":"workflow/#step-3-run-migrations","title":"Step 3: Run migrations","text":""},{"location":"workflow/#step-4-test-code-in-development-mode","title":"Step 4: Test code in development mode","text":""},{"location":"workflow/#step-5-switch-to-production-mode","title":"Step 5: Switch to production mode","text":""},{"location":"workflow/#step-6-configure-credentials-in-env-file","title":"Step 6: Configure Credentials in .env file","text":""},{"location":"workflow/#step-7-collect-static-files","title":"step 7: Collect static files","text":""},{"location":"workflow/#step-8-check-deploy-issues-misconfigurations","title":"Step 8: Check deploy issues (misconfigurations)","text":""},{"location":"workflow/#notedont-try-to-run-all-these-commmands-at-oncerun-one-by-one","title":"NOTE:Dont try to run all these commmands at once(run one by one)","text":""},{"location":"workflow/#development-workkflow","title":"Development workkflow","text":"<pre><code>django-facile startproject myproject --env dev --db sqlite\ncd myproject\ndjango-facile startapp blog\ndjango-facile migrate\ndjango-facile run\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"workflow/#production-workflow","title":"Production workflow","text":"<pre><code>\ndjango-facile switch-env prod\ndjango-facile migrate\ndjango-facile collectstatic\ndjango-facile check --deploy\n</code></pre>"}]}